02:29:20.040 --> 02:29:21.780
too, and they're just waiting for a

02:29:21.780 --> 02:29:22.979
chance to spring it on us.

02:29:23.040 --> 02:29:26.579
Snowfall rubbed her own wrists under the

02:29:26.579 --> 02:29:27.180
gift of stealth.

02:29:27.239 --> 02:29:29.219
In her dream last night.

02:29:29.280 --> 02:29:31.559
She'd been wearing a wrist cuff like all

02:29:31.559 --> 02:29:32.399
the silk wings.

02:29:32.459 --> 02:29:34.979
It was horribly heavy, she remembered

02:29:34.979 --> 02:29:35.159
now.

02:29:35.219 --> 02:29:39.659
She, Dream her, had felt as though it

02:29:39.659 --> 02:29:41.040
might drag her down into the ocean.

02:29:41.100 --> 02:29:43.500
There was an inscription on it that

02:29:43.500 --> 02:29:45.360
allowed her in and out of Yellow Jacket

02:29:45.360 --> 02:29:45.780
Hive.

02:29:45.840 --> 02:29:48.180
Yellow jacket hive.

02:29:48.239 --> 02:29:51.120
What a melodramatic name my dream brain

02:29:51.120 --> 02:29:51.780
came up with.

02:29:51.840 --> 02:29:54.899
Or probably I heard someone say it

02:29:54.899 --> 02:29:56.219
yesterday and just don't remember it.

