02:30:03.120 --> 02:30:06.360
Snowfall felt an irrational desire to run

02:30:06.360 --> 02:30:09.659
over and shake her, to yell, Luna's

02:30:09.659 --> 02:30:10.739
burning off the wrist cuffs.

