That's where the silk wings were to be

04:18:52.079 --> 04:18:54.479
kept until the breath of evil was ready

04:18:54.479 --> 04:18:54.840
for them.

04:18:54.899 --> 04:18:57.959
And I have to stand guard.

04:18:57.959 --> 04:19:01.139
Blue things. over my own friends and

04:19:01.139 --> 04:19:01.500
family.

