I can't even talk to them, or tell them I

04:19:04.860 --> 04:19:07.200
missed them, or then I'm sorry about

04:19:07.200 --> 04:19:07.500
this.

04:19:07.559 --> 04:19:11.520
When tears come, as they often do.

04:19:11.639 --> 04:19:14.340
He can't wipe them away, because his

04:19:14.340 --> 04:19:16.500
claws are not his claws.

04:19:16.559 --> 04:19:19.920
They're my claws.

04:19:19.979 --> 04:19:23.579
Oh, their claws are my claws.

04:19:23.639 --> 04:19:25.979
She enjoys looking through this little

04:19:25.979 --> 04:19:28.500
silk wing, the flame silk who dared to

04:19:28.500 --> 04:19:31.379
defy her, but she has a lot of dragons to

04:19:31.379 --> 04:19:33.959
wield, and can't stay entangled in anyone

04:19:33.959 --> 04:19:34.500
for too long.

