Sometimes, you have to work with monsters

04:20:06.899 --> 04:20:08.579
to get the power you want.

04:20:08.639 --> 04:20:12.299
Three tribes, all bowing to her.

04:20:12.360 --> 04:20:14.940
It's what she's wanted all along, isn't

04:20:14.940 --> 04:20:15.059
it?

