04:20:21.840 --> 04:20:23.520
They were different.

04:20:23.579 --> 04:20:27.299
Dangerous, strange and terrifying.

04:20:27.420 --> 04:20:31.379
Those tribes would have attacked me 1st

04:20:31.379 --> 04:20:33.059
if I hadn't attacked them.

04:20:33.120 --> 04:20:37.379
If everyone is evil, the only way to

04:20:37.379 --> 04:20:39.600
survive is to be the most evil.

04:20:39.659 --> 04:20:43.200
Silk wings and leaf wings are different

04:20:43.200 --> 04:20:46.260
from us and need to be controlled.

04:20:46.319 --> 04:20:50.219
As long as she controls everything, she'll

04:20:50.219 --> 04:20:50.579
be safe.

04:20:50.639 --> 04:20:52.680
Everyone will be safe.

04:20:52.739 --> 04:20:55.500
No one can threaten her when they can't

04:20:55.500 --> 04:20:57.059
even lift a claw against her.

04:20:57.180 --> 04:21:01.739
Everyone was out to get me, but I showed

04:21:01.739 --> 04:21:03.840
them, and now they're all mine.

04:21:03.899 --> 04:21:06.840
This is what it means to be a true

04:21:06.840 --> 04:21:07.500
queen.

04:21:07.559 --> 04:21:09.540
Complete control.

04:21:09.600 --> 04:21:11.399
Nothing to fear.

04:21:11.459 --> 04:21:15.299
No one to stop her or argue with her or

04:21:15.299 --> 04:21:16.200
complain about her.

04:21:16.260 --> 04:21:20.700
They fear her, and that is how it should

04:21:20.700 --> 04:21:21.000
be.

04:21:21.059 --> 04:21:25.500
She is pacing, and she realizes her

04:21:25.500 --> 04:21:27.120
thoughts are spiraling down an

04:21:27.120 --> 04:21:28.319
uncontrolled path again.

04:21:28.379 --> 04:21:30.719
She'll have to kill something to calm

04:21:30.719 --> 04:21:31.200
herself down.

04:21:31.260 --> 04:21:35.219
Snowfall was wrenched very suddenly out

04:21:35.219 --> 04:21:38.459
of wasp, and landed hard, painfully, back

04:21:38.459 --> 04:21:39.000
in her own mind.

04:21:39.059 --> 04:21:42.239
It felt as though she had just plummeted

04:21:42.239 --> 04:21:44.459
from a great height, and midway.

04:21:44.579 --> 04:21:46.559
She had turned from one dragon into

04:21:46.559 --> 04:21:48.659
another, completely different dragon.

04:21:48.719 --> 04:21:51.959
Or more like a 3rd dragon.

04:21:52.020 --> 04:21:55.200
Blue, to wasp, to me.

04:21:55.260 --> 04:21:58.379
Blue was the most opposite of herself

04:21:58.379 --> 04:22:01.020
she'd ever been, and the most powerless.

04:22:01.079 --> 04:22:04.139
It was awful, and she hated it.

04:22:04.200 --> 04:22:06.659
And she would never, never forgive the

04:22:06.659 --> 04:22:07.620
ring for doing this to her.

04:22:07.739 --> 04:22:09.780
But WASP?

04:22:09.959 --> 04:22:13.379
Wasp was worse, because Snowfall had

04:22:13.379 --> 04:22:15.780
heard echoes of her own fears inside

04:22:15.780 --> 04:22:16.860
Wasp's head.

04:22:16.920 --> 04:22:19.680
I'm not like her, am I?

04:22:19.799 --> 04:22:22.200
I would never make the choices she's

04:22:22.200 --> 04:22:22.379
made.

04:22:22.440 --> 04:22:24.239
Would I?

04:22:24.299 --> 04:22:28.440
Such as accepting a strange magic I don't

04:22:28.440 --> 04:22:30.600
know enough about, in order to make

04:22:30.600 --> 04:22:32.040
myself more powerful.

04:22:32.100 --> 04:22:34.920
Asked an uncomfortable part of her

04:22:34.920 --> 04:22:35.579
brain.

04:22:35.639 --> 04:22:39.299
She realized she was lying on grass, and

04:22:39.299 --> 04:22:41.219
her face was wet, as though someone had

04:22:41.219 --> 04:22:43.260
flung part of the wake over her head.

04:22:43.319 --> 04:22:46.319
The air smelled like scavengers and pine

04:22:46.319 --> 04:22:48.000
trees, and distant snow.

04:22:48.120 --> 04:22:51.059
She was definitely on her own continent

04:22:51.059 --> 04:22:51.239
again.

04:22:51.299 --> 04:22:54.540
I'm not wasp, or blue.

04:22:54.600 --> 04:22:57.180
I am me, and snowfall.

04:22:57.239 --> 04:22:59.159
I've always been snowfall.

04:22:59.219 --> 04:23:01.680
I don't want to be anyone else.

04:23:01.799 --> 04:23:03.120
Ever again.

04:23:03.180 --> 04:23:05.940
Someone was shaking her shoulder.

04:23:06.000 --> 04:23:08.100
Wake up.

04:23:08.159 --> 04:23:09.180
Please wake up.

04:23:09.239 --> 04:23:10.559
The someone said.

04:23:10.620 --> 04:23:12.059
Snowfall.

04:23:12.120 --> 04:23:13.079
Snowfall?

04:23:13.139 --> 04:23:16.620
That must be links, disrespectfully

04:23:16.620 --> 04:23:18.120
forgetting how a queen should be

04:23:18.120 --> 04:23:19.260
addressed, again.

04:23:19.319 --> 04:23:22.020
Snowfall cracked her eyes open.

04:23:22.079 --> 04:23:25.020
