Got taken over by a stupid magic vision.

04:23:32.399 --> 04:23:35.159
Oh, no.

04:23:35.280 --> 04:23:38.100
That wasn't supposed to happen.

04:23:38.159 --> 04:23:40.559
A vision in the middle of the day?

04:23:40.620 --> 04:23:42.000
When she was wide awake?

