Ugh, horrifying.

04:24:55.020 --> 04:24:58.620
Cricket was perhaps a scale closer to

04:24:58.620 --> 04:25:01.139
snowfalls type than grayling, but still

04:25:01.139 --> 04:25:02.340
several continents off.

