crouching a little lower to the grass.

04:25:49.319 --> 04:25:52.440
Her claw hurt from her violent attempts

04:25:52.440 --> 04:25:54.840
to pull off the ring, and her head still

04:25:54.840 --> 04:25:57.540
ached from being yanked out of wasp, and

04:25:57.540 --> 04:25:59.459
she had a weird, flippy feeling in her

04:25:59.459 --> 04:26:01.079
stomach that had no reasonable

04:26:01.079 --> 04:26:04.079
