Winter said to Luna.

04:26:30.000 --> 04:26:31.379
Only Night Wings.

04:26:31.440 --> 04:26:35.219
But that looked like magic, Kibley said.

04:26:35.280 --> 04:26:38.280
He glanced at Thorn, as if she had the

04:26:38.280 --> 04:26:39.360
eyes he trusted the most.

04:26:39.420 --> 04:26:40.860
Didn't it?

04:26:40.920 --> 04:26:43.440
Like something magic just happened to

04:26:43.440 --> 04:26:44.219
Queen Snowfall?

