04:26:58.920 --> 04:27:01.559
soccer, and the plague, and what had

04:27:01.559 --> 04:27:04.200
happened to the last ice wing queen, and

04:27:04.200 --> 04:27:06.239
other unknown evil spells that might be

04:27:06.239 --> 04:27:06.840
