04:27:57.059 --> 04:28:00.120
Her gaze going from snowfall to Lynx to

04:28:00.120 --> 04:28:01.319
Kibley and Thorn.

04:28:01.379 --> 04:28:02.700
They do.

04:28:02.760 --> 04:28:05.280
Like the invisible Ice Wing Army

04:28:05.280 --> 04:28:06.180
remember?

04:28:06.239 --> 04:28:07.079
I told you about that?

