They both looked startled, and a little

07:18:24.060 --> 07:18:26.340
nervous, but those were expressions she

07:18:26.340 --> 07:18:28.080
was pretty used to seeing on her own ice

07:18:28.080 --> 07:18:28.799
wings by now.

07:18:28.860 --> 07:18:30.599
She'd work on that.

07:18:30.659 --> 07:18:33.479
Low voices were coming from the throne

07:18:33.479 --> 07:18:35.759
room, so Snowfall headed there first.

07:18:35.819 --> 07:18:38.580
That was sort of suspicious, actually.

07:18:38.639 --> 07:18:41.220
Why would anyone be in the throne room

07:18:41.220 --> 07:18:41.819
while she was away?

07:18:41.880 --> 07:18:45.779
Don't be paranoid, she reminded herself.

07:18:45.840 --> 07:18:47.880
Not everyone is out to get me.

07:18:47.939 --> 07:18:50.099
I am not Queen Wasp.

07:18:50.159 --> 07:18:53.580
She swept through the window and landed

07:18:53.580 --> 07:18:55.200
right in the center of the grand room.

07:18:55.259 --> 07:18:58.680
Conversation slammed to a halt. all

07:18:58.680 --> 07:18:59.099
around her.

07:18:59.159 --> 07:19:02.459
On one side of the throne stood general

07:19:02.459 --> 07:19:05.159
ivory, flanked by a few soldiers, looking

07:19:05.159 --> 07:19:06.540
fierce and bristly.

07:19:06.599 --> 07:19:08.939
On the other side were tundra and

07:19:08.939 --> 07:19:09.840
permafrost.

07:19:09.900 --> 07:19:12.599
Calm and gleaming and toothy.

07:19:12.720 --> 07:19:15.540
And on the throne itself, wearing

07:19:15.540 --> 07:19:18.180
Snowfall's hideous crown was her little

07:19:18.180 --> 07:19:19.500
sister, Mink.

07:19:19.619 --> 07:19:22.680
Snowfall raised her eyebrows at the

07:19:22.680 --> 07:19:23.759
gathered dragons.

07:19:23.759 --> 07:19:25.979
Hello, Mink, she said.

07:19:26.099 --> 07:19:28.200
That's way too big for you.

07:19:28.319 --> 07:19:31.560
Mink reached up and clutched the crown to

07:19:31.560 --> 07:19:31.979
her head.

07:19:32.040 --> 07:19:33.959
Her giant eyes blinking quickly.

07:19:34.020 --> 07:19:38.220
We thought you weren't coming back, Tundra

07:19:38.220 --> 07:19:40.380
said, in her slippery, well blubber

07:19:40.380 --> 07:19:40.860
voice.

07:19:40.919 --> 07:19:44.099
I said she was, Ivory growled.

07:19:44.159 --> 07:19:45.419
You wouldn't listen.

07:19:45.479 --> 07:19:49.380
We thought it was highly unlikely that

07:19:49.380 --> 07:19:51.419
you'd leave a lonely soldier in charge

07:19:51.419 --> 07:19:52.680
rather than one of us.

07:19:52.799 --> 07:19:55.860
Permafrost smarmed, flicking his tail

07:19:55.860 --> 07:19:57.060
between himself and tundra.

07:19:57.180 --> 07:20:00.720
So, we assumed something terrible must

07:20:00.720 --> 07:20:01.500
have happened to you.

07:20:01.619 --> 07:20:03.419
You were wrong.

07:20:03.479 --> 07:20:06.240
Snowfall said pleasantly, and now

07:20:06.240 --> 07:20:08.040
something terrible is going to happen to

07:20:08.040 --> 07:20:08.220
you.

07:20:08.279 --> 07:20:10.200
Thank you for trying, Ivory.

07:20:10.259 --> 07:20:11.279
Mink?

07:20:11.340 --> 07:20:12.119
Budge over.

07:20:12.180 --> 07:20:12.840
That's my seat.

07:20:12.959 --> 07:20:16.919
No Mink yelled, bursting into tears.

07:20:16.979 --> 07:20:19.259
I have to be queen.

07:20:19.319 --> 07:20:21.479
I have to stop the awful, hateful

07:20:21.479 --> 07:20:23.400
terrible, bad, night wings.

07:20:23.520 --> 07:20:26.520
Snowfall squinted at her, then exchanged

07:20:26.520 --> 07:20:27.900
a puzzled glance with links.

07:20:28.020 --> 07:20:29.340
The what?

07:20:29.400 --> 07:20:30.119
she asked.

07:20:30.180 --> 07:20:32.580
The night wings.

07:20:32.639 --> 07:20:33.840
Mink sobbed.

07:20:33.900 --> 07:20:36.779
I hate them so m much.

07:20:36.840 --> 07:20:38.459
They're going to hurt us.

07:20:38.520 --> 07:20:39.900
Well.

07:20:40.020 --> 07:20:42.479
So this made no sense at all.

07:20:42.540 --> 07:20:45.119
Mink had never mentioned Nightwings

07:20:45.119 --> 07:20:47.099
before, that snowfall could remember.

07:20:47.159 --> 07:20:49.740
And Mink loved everybody.

07:20:49.979 --> 07:20:52.619
It didn't even seem possible for Mink to

07:20:52.619 --> 07:20:53.340
hate someone.

07:20:53.400 --> 07:20:55.200
Let alone an entire tribe.

07:20:55.259 --> 07:20:57.959
Was it something I said?

07:20:58.020 --> 07:21:00.779
Snowfall tried to remember, but she

07:21:00.779 --> 07:21:02.159
thought she would have noticed if she'd

07:21:02.159 --> 07:21:05.340
said, the night wings are the worst, Mink

07:21:05.340 --> 07:21:07.139
and Mink had said, yeah, let's hate

07:21:07.139 --> 07:21:07.380
them.

07:21:07.439 --> 07:21:09.779
Did you do this?

07:21:09.840 --> 07:21:12.360
She asked tundra and permafrost.

07:21:12.419 --> 07:21:14.400
Did you make her afraid of the night

07:21:14.400 --> 07:21:14.819
wings?

07:21:14.880 --> 07:21:17.159
Tundra lifted her wings.

07:21:17.220 --> 07:21:19.500
We haven't said anything about them.

07:21:19.619 --> 07:21:21.479
I don't know where this came from.

07:21:21.540 --> 07:21:25.139
Snowfall was inclined not to believe her

07:21:25.139 --> 07:21:28.139
but Tundra looked as confused as Snowfall

07:21:28.139 --> 07:21:30.360
felt, and it was rare to see her aunt

07:21:30.360 --> 07:21:32.340
have an actual emotion on her face.

07:21:32.400 --> 07:21:34.979
When did she start talking about them?

07:21:35.040 --> 07:21:38.520
The moment we made her queen, Tundra

07:21:38.520 --> 07:21:38.759
said.

07:21:38.819 --> 07:21:41.880
I mean, temporary queen, of course.

07:21:41.939 --> 07:21:44.159
Just in case you weren't returning.

07:21:44.220 --> 07:21:46.080
Uh-huh.

07:21:46.139 --> 07:21:48.540
A queen you could control a little better

07:21:48.540 --> 07:21:49.740
than me, I suppose.

07:21:49.799 --> 07:21:51.540
Snowfall thought.

07:21:51.599 --> 07:21:54.659
So where did Mink get this new fear of

07:21:54.659 --> 07:21:55.500
night wings?

07:21:55.560 --> 07:21:57.720
If Tundra hadn't said anything.

07:21:57.840 --> 07:22:01.439
But somehow when she became queen.

07:22:01.500 --> 07:22:05.220
Snowfall strode across the room and

07:22:05.220 --> 07:22:07.139
knocked the crown off Mink's head.

07:22:07.200 --> 07:22:10.380
Mink yelped and tried to grab for it, but

07:22:10.380 --> 07:22:12.659
Snowfall held her at arm's length with

07:22:12.659 --> 07:22:14.459
the crown in her other talon.

07:22:14.520 --> 07:22:17.159
Aunt Tundra, she said.

07:22:17.220 --> 07:22:19.080
What do you know about this crown?

07:22:19.139 --> 07:22:20.220
When was it made?

07:22:20.279 --> 07:22:23.700
It's been in the royal family for 100s of

07:22:23.700 --> 07:22:26.459
years, Tendra said, sounding quite

07:22:26.459 --> 07:22:27.240
scandalized.

07:22:27.299 --> 07:22:30.180
It's one of the most treasured ice swing

07:22:30.180 --> 07:22:30.720
heirlooms.

07:22:30.779 --> 07:22:32.759
Yes, yes.

07:22:32.819 --> 07:22:35.279
Snowfall said, but who made it?

07:22:35.400 --> 07:22:38.459
Tundra looked at permafrost, who

07:22:38.459 --> 07:22:39.840
scratched his neck and mumbled.

07:22:39.959 --> 07:22:41.700
I'm not sure.

07:22:41.759 --> 07:22:45.240
I believe maybe it's from the time of

07:22:45.240 --> 07:22:45.900
Queen Diamond.

07:22:45.959 --> 07:22:47.939
Queen Diamond.

07:22:48.000 --> 07:22:49.380
Snowfall said.

07:22:49.500 --> 07:22:52.200
As in the one whose son ran off with a

07:22:52.200 --> 07:22:55.439
night wing, was kidnapped by a night

07:22:55.439 --> 07:22:55.860
wing.

07:22:55.919 --> 07:22:57.299
Tundra objected.

07:22:57.360 --> 07:23:00.419
The queen who happened to be an animus

07:23:00.419 --> 07:23:02.159
herself, Snowfall said.

07:23:02.220 --> 07:23:03.240
Correct.

07:23:03.360 --> 07:23:06.240
Oh, length cried.

07:23:06.360 --> 07:23:09.659
Tundra shot her a quelling look, but Lynx

07:23:09.659 --> 07:23:11.459
ignored her, taking a step towards

07:23:11.459 --> 07:23:12.180
snowfall.

07:23:12.240 --> 07:23:15.180
You think the crown could be enchanted, to

07:23:15.180 --> 07:23:17.279
make every queen who wears it hate night

07:23:17.279 --> 07:23:18.720
wings as much as Diamond did.

07:23:18.779 --> 07:23:21.180
But nobody knew it for all this time.

07:23:21.240 --> 07:23:23.580
That's awful.

07:23:23.639 --> 07:23:26.459
Permafrost flapped his jaw for a moment

07:23:26.459 --> 07:23:29.040
as if a sealskin rug had come back to

07:23:29.040 --> 07:23:31.380
life and started questioning his moral

07:23:31.380 --> 07:23:31.740
authority.

07:23:31.799 --> 07:23:35.759
It's true Queen Diamond was an animus, he

07:23:35.759 --> 07:23:39.180
said, but, but she wouldn't just.

07:23:39.299 --> 07:23:42.779
That is, she couldn't use her power

07:23:42.779 --> 07:23:44.520
beyond her one gift to the tribe.

07:23:44.639 --> 07:23:46.200
She wouldn't.

07:23:46.319 --> 07:23:47.279
I'm sure of it.

07:23:47.340 --> 07:23:50.639
Well, I'm not, Snowfall said.

07:23:50.700 --> 07:23:52.500
And I don't like this thing anyway.

07:23:52.619 --> 07:23:55.979
So let's be safe and fashionable and

07:23:55.979 --> 07:23:56.580
destroy it.

07:23:56.639 --> 07:23:58.619
Destroy it?

07:23:58.680 --> 07:24:00.779
Tundra gasped faintly.

07:24:00.840 --> 07:24:03.540
Ooh, we can do that?

07:24:03.599 --> 07:24:04.799
Main gasp.

07:24:04.860 --> 07:24:06.900
Because I really, really don't like it

07:24:06.900 --> 07:24:07.919
either, Snowfall.

07:24:07.979 --> 07:24:09.659
It's so heavy.

07:24:09.720 --> 07:24:10.439
It hurt my head.

07:24:10.500 --> 07:24:11.639
Did it hurt yours?

07:24:11.700 --> 07:24:15.840
Yes, it hurt my head a lot, Snowfall told

07:24:15.840 --> 07:24:16.080
her.

07:24:16.139 --> 07:24:18.659
Ivory, would you take charge of

07:24:18.659 --> 07:24:19.560
destroying this for me?

07:24:19.680 --> 07:24:23.700
At once, Your Majesty, Ivory said, with a

07:24:23.700 --> 07:24:25.020
respectful bow.

07:24:25.080 --> 07:24:27.479
She lifted the crown out of Snowfall's

07:24:27.479 --> 07:24:29.939
talons and flew out of the room with 2 of

07:24:29.939 --> 07:24:30.479
her soldiers.

07:24:30.540 --> 07:24:33.900
Snowfall climbed up on the throne next to

07:24:33.900 --> 07:24:34.319
Mink.

07:24:34.380 --> 07:24:37.979
It was big enough for a very old queen, so

07:24:37.979 --> 07:24:39.659
there was enough room for her to scoot in

07:24:39.659 --> 07:24:40.439
beside her sister.

07:24:40.560 --> 07:24:43.560
She put one of her wings around Mink, who

07:24:43.560 --> 07:24:46.139
snuggled into her side, closed her eyes

07:24:46.139 --> 07:24:47.639
and sighed with relief.

07:24:47.639 --> 07:24:50.279
I don't have to be queen.

07:24:50.400 --> 07:24:51.599
Mink whispered.

07:24:51.720 --> 07:24:54.180
You are not allowed to be queen right

07:24:54.180 --> 07:24:54.419
now.

07:24:54.479 --> 07:24:56.159
Snowfall said kindly.

07:24:56.220 --> 07:24:58.680
I'm going to be queen for a long time.

07:24:58.740 --> 07:25:01.319
Good, Mink said.

07:25:01.439 --> 07:25:04.740
I'm sorry so many dragons keep telling

07:25:04.740 --> 07:25:05.580
you what to do, though.

07:25:05.639 --> 07:25:07.919
That was my least favorite part.

07:25:07.979 --> 07:25:11.220
It'll be better if it's the rye dragons

07:25:11.220 --> 07:25:12.119
snowfall said.

07:25:12.180 --> 07:25:14.639
I just have to ignore the ones I don't

07:25:14.639 --> 07:25:15.000
trust.

07:25:15.060 --> 07:25:18.779
She shot a significant look at tundra and

07:25:18.779 --> 07:25:19.439
permafrost.

07:25:19.500 --> 07:25:21.840
The crown was magic.

07:25:21.900 --> 07:25:23.220
Mink asked.

07:25:23.279 --> 07:25:25.500
Does that mean I don't have to hate the

07:25:25.500 --> 07:25:26.220
night wings?

07:25:26.279 --> 07:25:27.720
That's right.

07:25:27.779 --> 07:25:29.459
It was just a spell.

07:25:29.520 --> 07:25:32.040
Snowfall bopped Mink's head with her

07:25:32.040 --> 07:25:32.400
snout.

07:25:32.459 --> 07:25:34.139
It'll wear off.

07:25:34.200 --> 07:25:36.240
I feel much better about night wings

07:25:36.240 --> 07:25:38.099
after being away from the crown for a few

07:25:38.099 --> 07:25:38.279
days.

07:25:38.340 --> 07:25:41.819
Plus, I bet if you meet any, you'll love

07:25:41.819 --> 07:25:43.680
them immediately, just like you love

07:25:43.680 --> 07:25:44.279
everybody else.

07:25:44.340 --> 07:25:48.119
Oh, I'd like that, Mink said.

07:25:48.180 --> 07:25:50.340
I love you the most, though.

07:25:50.459 --> 07:25:52.439
Snowball laughed.

07:25:52.560 --> 07:25:55.799
I met a sky wing, you would adore, she

07:25:55.799 --> 07:25:56.099
said.

07:25:56.159 --> 07:25:58.619
I didn't realize until right now that he

07:25:58.619 --> 07:25:59.459
reminded me of you.

07:25:59.520 --> 07:26:04.439
Your majesty, Tundra said frostily, as

07:26:04.439 --> 07:26:06.299
the wall has been neglected for a number

07:26:06.299 --> 07:26:09.540
of days, despite my best efforts.

07:26:09.659 --> 07:26:11.880
Perhaps you would appreciate a few

07:26:11.880 --> 07:26:14.340
updates about the behavior of the palace

07:26:14.340 --> 07:26:16.200
ice wings in your absence.

07:26:16.439 --> 07:26:19.860
Ah, yes, Snowfall said.

07:26:19.919 --> 07:26:21.479
Thank you for reminding me.

07:26:21.540 --> 07:26:24.180
Mink, want to see something cool?

07:26:24.240 --> 07:26:26.520
I do, I do.

07:26:26.639 --> 07:26:28.259
Mink sang.

07:26:28.319 --> 07:26:30.240
A snowfall led her through the halls and

07:26:30.240 --> 07:26:31.200
out into the courtyard.

07:26:31.259 --> 07:26:34.319
Tundra trailed after them, protesting

07:26:34.319 --> 07:26:35.580
that the queen needed more information

07:26:35.580 --> 07:26:37.560
before she started rearranging names.

07:26:37.680 --> 07:26:40.439
Permafrost had made themselves scarce

07:26:40.439 --> 07:26:43.259
perhaps realizing that the farther out of

07:26:43.259 --> 07:26:45.659
Snowfall's side he was, the fewer spots

07:26:45.659 --> 07:26:47.099
he'd drop on the list.

07:26:47.159 --> 07:26:49.799
There were several ice wings out in the

07:26:49.799 --> 07:26:52.439
courtyard, gathered near the wall or on

07:26:52.439 --> 07:26:54.299
benches, chatting to one another.

07:26:54.360 --> 07:26:57.119
A hush spread through them as snowfall

07:26:57.119 --> 07:26:59.759
swept by, and she saw a few starting to

07:26:59.759 --> 07:27:01.200
edge toward the nearest doors.

07:27:01.259 --> 07:27:05.639
Mink, Snowfall said, stopping beside the

07:27:05.639 --> 07:27:06.299
gift of order.

07:27:06.360 --> 07:27:07.799
Do you know what this is?

07:27:07.919 --> 07:27:11.700
Of course I do, Mink said with wide

07:27:11.700 --> 07:27:12.060
eyes.

07:27:12.119 --> 07:27:14.700
Everybody knows what the wall is.

07:27:14.759 --> 07:27:16.740
Look, there's me.

07:27:16.799 --> 07:27:19.439
She pointed to her name on the dragonette

07:27:19.439 --> 07:27:19.740
side.

07:27:19.860 --> 07:27:21.060
I'm here.

07:27:21.119 --> 07:27:24.299
Which means those dragons up there are

07:27:24.299 --> 07:27:25.020
better than me.

07:27:25.080 --> 07:27:28.919
But I'm still better than this dragon, and

07:27:28.919 --> 07:27:31.919
this dragon, and this dragon, and this

07:27:31.919 --> 07:27:36.119
dragon, and all these dragons, she said

07:27:36.119 --> 07:27:38.040
tapping one name after another below

07:27:38.040 --> 07:27:38.400
hers.

07:27:38.459 --> 07:27:40.979
Snowfall winced.

07:27:41.040 --> 07:27:43.439
It was somehow so much worse to hear

07:27:43.439 --> 07:27:45.119
something like that from someone as

07:27:45.119 --> 07:27:46.500
little and sweet as mink.

07:27:46.560 --> 07:27:49.740
That's what I thought too, she said to

07:27:49.740 --> 07:27:50.159
her sister.

07:27:50.220 --> 07:27:52.919
But it turns out, that makes no sense.

07:27:52.979 --> 07:27:55.380
It makes no sense.

07:27:55.439 --> 07:27:57.959
Mink echoed, blinking up at her.

07:27:58.020 --> 07:28:00.840
You might do better on a math test than

07:28:00.840 --> 07:28:04.020
this dragon, Snowfall said, pointing to a

07:28:04.020 --> 07:28:04.979
name below minx.

07:28:05.040 --> 07:28:07.740
But what if he carves a better Isis

07:28:07.740 --> 07:28:08.220
sculpture than you?

07:28:08.340 --> 07:28:10.380
Then who should be higher on the list?

07:28:10.439 --> 07:28:12.299
What?

07:28:12.360 --> 07:28:13.919
Mink cried outraged.

07:28:13.979 --> 07:28:15.900
But better than mine?

07:28:15.959 --> 07:28:16.560
Where?

07:28:16.619 --> 07:28:17.340
I want to see.

07:28:17.400 --> 07:28:21.479
I just mean if he did, Snowfall said.

07:28:21.540 --> 07:28:24.060
Hmm, Mink said.

07:28:24.119 --> 07:28:25.439
Not possible.

07:28:25.500 --> 07:28:28.979
But I love you anyway, polar bear, she

07:28:28.979 --> 07:28:30.959
shouted, at one of the little faces

07:28:30.959 --> 07:28:32.520
peeking out of a window overhead.

07:28:32.639 --> 07:28:36.840
What I mean, Snowfall said, is that if

07:28:36.840 --> 07:28:38.520
you spend all your time worrying about

07:28:38.520 --> 07:28:41.099
where you are on the list, and who's

07:28:41.099 --> 07:28:42.840
higher than you, and who's below you.

07:28:42.959 --> 07:28:46.500
You can't focus on what you do well. or

07:28:46.500 --> 07:28:48.599
how everybody can do something important

07:28:48.599 --> 07:28:51.720
or kind or clever, no matter where they

07:28:51.720 --> 07:28:52.380
are on the list.

07:28:52.500 --> 07:28:55.139
And maybe you start to think the dragons

07:28:55.139 --> 07:28:57.779
below you aren't as important or special

07:28:57.779 --> 07:28:59.520
as you are, which is silly.

07:28:59.580 --> 07:29:02.759
Hmm, Mink said thoughtfully.

07:29:02.880 --> 07:29:05.459
She tipped her head up again and yelled

07:29:05.459 --> 07:29:06.659
Polar bear.

07:29:06.720 --> 07:29:08.400
I think you're very special and

07:29:08.400 --> 07:29:09.000
important.

07:29:09.119 --> 07:29:11.580
Thank you, he called back.

07:29:11.639 --> 07:29:15.060
Snowfall wasn't sure this lesson was

07:29:15.060 --> 07:29:17.099
going quite as well as she'd pictured it

07:29:17.099 --> 07:29:17.400
in her head.

07:29:17.459 --> 07:29:21.060
Maybe she should break stuff 1st, explain

07:29:21.060 --> 07:29:21.599
it all later.

07:29:21.659 --> 07:29:25.259
She called up the tiara's strength and

07:29:25.259 --> 07:29:27.299
slammed her fist into the wall of names.

07:29:27.360 --> 07:29:31.080
Cracks shot out in all directions, like

07:29:31.080 --> 07:29:33.360
bolts of lightning, ripping through every

07:29:33.360 --> 07:29:34.319
name on the list.

07:29:34.380 --> 07:29:38.099
Tundra shrieked in horror, and tried to

07:29:38.099 --> 07:29:40.619
grab her arm, but Snowfall shook her off

07:29:40.619 --> 07:29:43.319
easily and did it again, and then again

07:29:43.319 --> 07:29:45.779
smashing the wall until it was

07:29:45.779 --> 07:29:48.419
obliterated, and she was surrounded by a

07:29:48.419 --> 07:29:50.220
rubble of broken chunks of ice.

07:29:50.279 --> 07:29:54.840
Whew, she said, into the cloud of

07:29:54.840 --> 07:29:56.279
glittering ice dust around her.

07:29:56.340 --> 07:29:57.779
That's better.

07:29:57.840 --> 07:30:02.459
But, but, Tundra cried.

07:30:02.520 --> 07:30:05.400
Snowfall realized that lynx was standing

07:30:05.400 --> 07:30:08.040
between them, wings spread, to stop

07:30:08.040 --> 07:30:10.619
tundra from charging at snowfall again.

07:30:10.680 --> 07:30:13.200
Tundra seemed unable to move at the

07:30:13.200 --> 07:30:13.619
moment, though.

07:30:13.680 --> 07:30:16.259
She was staring at the space where the

07:30:16.259 --> 07:30:18.360
wall had been, as though she thought it

07:30:18.360 --> 07:30:21.119
might magically rebuild itself if she

07:30:21.119 --> 07:30:22.139
stared hard enough.

07:30:22.200 --> 07:30:23.700
Can it do that?

07:30:23.759 --> 07:30:27.060
Snowfall gave the broken bits of eyes a

07:30:27.060 --> 07:30:27.959
hard stare of her own.

07:30:28.020 --> 07:30:30.000
They stayed where they were.

07:30:30.060 --> 07:30:32.459
No sign of any magical rebuilding.

07:30:32.520 --> 07:30:36.000
Don't even try it, ancient ice wall.

07:30:36.119 --> 07:30:39.900
As the echoes died away, lynx started

07:30:39.900 --> 07:30:40.500
clapping.

07:30:40.619 --> 07:30:43.979
Mink immediately joined in, beaming

07:30:43.979 --> 07:30:45.959
although snowfall suspected she just

07:30:45.959 --> 07:30:47.639
loved clapping, and didn't entirely

07:30:47.639 --> 07:30:50.159
understand the enormity of what snowfall

07:30:50.159 --> 07:30:50.459
had done.

07:30:50.520 --> 07:30:54.180
I just smashed centuries of tradition

07:30:54.180 --> 07:30:57.540
into literal pieces, she thought, feeling

07:30:57.540 --> 07:30:58.380
a little dizzy.

07:30:58.439 --> 07:31:01.919
But then another ice wing started to clap

07:31:01.919 --> 07:31:04.560
and another, across the courtyard.

07:31:04.619 --> 07:31:07.319
Snowfall saw a few more at their windows

07:31:07.319 --> 07:31:09.659
applauding, although she also saw some

07:31:09.659 --> 07:31:11.639
older dragons duck out of sight when she

07:31:11.639 --> 07:31:13.740
looked, as though they didn't want to be

07:31:13.740 --> 07:31:15.959
caught with disapproving expressions on.

07:31:16.020 --> 07:31:17.939
It's all right.

07:31:18.000 --> 07:31:20.340
Eventually they'll see that it's better

07:31:20.340 --> 07:31:20.759
this way.

07:31:20.819 --> 07:31:23.040
The gift.

07:31:23.099 --> 07:31:27.540
Of order, Tundra said faintly, and then

07:31:27.540 --> 07:31:28.799
she collapsed into the snow.

07:31:28.860 --> 07:31:32.279
Snowfall beckoned 2 of her guards over

07:31:32.279 --> 07:31:34.439
and told them to carry Tundra gently to

07:31:34.439 --> 07:31:37.380
her room and stay until she recovered, in

07:31:37.380 --> 07:31:38.220
case she needed anything.

07:31:38.279 --> 07:31:41.099
This is so exciting.

07:31:41.159 --> 07:31:44.220
Mink said to Snowfall, scrambling over

07:31:44.220 --> 07:31:45.119
and sitting on her foot.

07:31:45.180 --> 07:31:47.099
What else can we break?

07:31:47.159 --> 07:31:48.959
Can I smash something next?

07:31:49.020 --> 07:31:53.279
Maybe tomorrow, Snowfall said, resting

07:31:53.279 --> 07:31:54.479
one wing around her sister.

07:31:54.540 --> 07:31:56.880
I'll let you wear my tiara and

07:31:56.880 --> 07:31:57.119
everything.

07:31:57.240 --> 07:32:00.060
Tonight, I think, I need to have some ice

07:32:00.060 --> 07:32:01.259
cream and go to sleep.

07:32:01.319 --> 07:32:04.020
Snowflakes were drifting from the gray

07:32:04.020 --> 07:32:06.240
sky, covering everything in quiet

07:32:06.240 --> 07:32:06.959
sparkles.

07:32:07.020 --> 07:32:10.740
I love it when I'm right, Lang said.

07:32:10.799 --> 07:32:13.200
Snowfall bristled at her.

07:32:13.259 --> 07:32:14.700
Who said you were?

07:32:14.759 --> 07:32:17.340
Maybe I smashed it for my own reasons.

07:32:17.400 --> 07:32:19.560
I have many opinions that have nothing to

07:32:19.560 --> 07:32:19.979
do with you.

07:32:20.099 --> 07:32:22.860
Links gave her a sideways grin.

07:32:22.979 --> 07:32:24.599
What?

07:32:24.659 --> 07:32:25.619
Snfall said.

07:32:25.680 --> 07:32:27.060
Did you mean something else?

07:32:27.180 --> 07:32:28.860
Ride about what?

07:32:28.919 --> 07:32:31.200
Links flicked her tail gently at

07:32:31.200 --> 07:32:32.159
Snowfall's wings.

07:32:32.220 --> 07:32:35.880
About you being the best queen ever, Madam

07:32:35.880 --> 07:32:36.720
Spiky Face.

07:32:36.779 --> 07:32:37.979
Oh.

07:32:38.040 --> 07:32:41.099
Snowfall resettled her spikes and nodded

07:32:41.099 --> 07:32:41.639
regally.

07:32:41.700 --> 07:32:42.840
Yes.

07:32:42.900 --> 07:32:44.880
Well, that is the plan.

07:32:45.000 --> 07:32:49.680
Chapter 24.

07:32:49.919 --> 07:32:52.439
She opens her eyes.

07:32:52.500 --> 07:32:55.139
She is standing in the forbidden

07:32:55.139 --> 07:32:55.740
treasury.

07:32:55.799 --> 07:32:58.680
She can't see a light globe anywhere, but

07:32:58.680 --> 07:33:01.200
the niche's glow pale blue, and the walls

07:33:01.200 --> 07:33:03.479
glimmer as though icy fireflies are

07:33:03.479 --> 07:33:04.080
swimming through them.

07:33:04.200 --> 07:33:06.119
She is herself.

07:33:06.180 --> 07:33:08.159
She is Queen Snowfall.

07:33:08.220 --> 07:33:11.580
She feels that she is, but she holds her

07:33:11.580 --> 07:33:13.860
talons out and turns them over, just to

07:33:13.860 --> 07:33:14.159
be sure.

07:33:14.220 --> 07:33:17.400
The opal ring is still there, on her

07:33:17.400 --> 07:33:17.819
claw.

07:33:17.939 --> 07:33:20.340
She took off everything else before bed

07:33:20.340 --> 07:33:20.759
though.

07:33:20.819 --> 07:33:23.040
The tiara and all her weapons.

07:33:23.099 --> 07:33:24.959
This is her palace.

07:33:25.020 --> 07:33:26.159
She is the queen.

07:33:26.279 --> 07:33:28.740
And she decided she wasn't going to be

07:33:28.740 --> 07:33:30.299
afraid all the time anymore.

07:33:30.360 --> 07:33:34.979
But, She is having a vision, isn't she?

07:33:35.099 --> 07:33:37.560
How can she be having a vision of

07:33:37.560 --> 07:33:38.040
herself?

07:33:38.159 --> 07:33:40.979
Because this is the last one.

07:33:41.040 --> 07:33:42.900
Says a voice behind her.

07:33:42.959 --> 07:33:45.240
Snowfall turns.

07:33:45.360 --> 07:33:48.360
An ice wing is standing there, next to

07:33:48.360 --> 07:33:50.759
the empty niche labeled Gift of Vision.

07:33:50.880 --> 07:33:54.419
Even in the weird light, Snowfall can see

07:33:54.419 --> 07:33:57.060
that she has unusual scales, like there's

07:33:57.060 --> 07:33:59.159
a hint of another color beyond the white

07:33:59.159 --> 07:33:59.759
in each one.

07:33:59.880 --> 07:34:01.979
Like an opal.

07:34:02.099 --> 07:34:04.380
The dragon smiles.

07:34:04.439 --> 07:34:06.779
That's me, Opal.

07:34:06.840 --> 07:34:08.939
Nice to meet you, Queen Snowfall.

07:34:09.000 --> 07:34:11.159
Snowfall gives her a wry look.

07:34:11.220 --> 07:34:13.860
I have a feeling I've been yelling at you

07:34:13.860 --> 07:34:14.939
for the last several days.

07:34:15.000 --> 07:34:17.939
Opal shrugs her wings elegantly.

07:34:18.000 --> 07:34:20.639
No more than any of the queens who use

07:34:20.639 --> 07:34:21.299
the ring before you.

07:34:21.360 --> 07:34:23.279
Have there been a lot?

07:34:23.400 --> 07:34:24.779
Snowfall asks.

07:34:24.840 --> 07:34:27.240
Does every queen put it on at some

07:34:27.240 --> 07:34:27.479
point?

07:34:27.540 --> 07:34:29.220
Not everyone.

07:34:29.279 --> 07:34:30.599
Obal answers.

07:34:30.659 --> 07:34:33.060
It's enchanted to appear to those who

07:34:33.060 --> 07:34:33.599
need it most.

07:34:33.659 --> 07:34:36.599
Snowfall regards the ring for a moment.

07:34:36.659 --> 07:34:41.040
So I needed it because We had to find out

07:34:41.040 --> 07:34:42.659
what was happening in Pantala.

07:34:42.720 --> 07:34:45.479
And make a connection with the scavengers

07:34:45.479 --> 07:34:48.119
so they'd help us defeat Queen Wasp.

07:34:48.240 --> 07:34:49.919
Opal laughs.

07:34:49.979 --> 07:34:52.979
I'm glad you used it so well, she says.

07:34:53.040 --> 07:34:56.400
But no, it's for dragons who become queen

07:34:56.400 --> 07:34:58.139
before they are ready, to help them take

07:34:58.139 --> 07:34:59.700
steps toward becoming even stronger

07:34:59.700 --> 07:35:00.180
queens.

07:35:00.240 --> 07:35:03.119
Snowfall raises an eyebrow at her.

07:35:03.180 --> 07:35:05.819
That's a polite way of putting it, she

07:35:05.819 --> 07:35:06.299
says.

07:35:06.360 --> 07:35:09.180
But you mean it's for queens who are a

07:35:09.180 --> 07:35:11.099
total mess. to teach them to see the

07:35:11.099 --> 07:35:13.500
world through other dragon's eyes, so

07:35:13.500 --> 07:35:14.819
they won't be so selfish.

07:35:14.880 --> 07:35:16.200
Isn't that it?

07:35:16.259 --> 07:35:18.900
We don't say that part out loud.

07:35:18.900 --> 07:35:22.139
Oble admonishes her, but she's clearly

07:35:22.139 --> 07:35:22.799
hiding a smile.

07:35:22.919 --> 07:35:25.740
And you weren't a total mess.

07:35:25.799 --> 07:35:27.659
Are you really here?

07:35:27.720 --> 07:35:30.599
Snowfall asks, in the forbidden

07:35:30.599 --> 07:35:31.020
treasury.

07:35:31.080 --> 07:35:33.599
Just wondering how to find you so I can

07:35:33.599 --> 07:35:34.860
throw you in my dungeon forever.

07:35:34.919 --> 07:35:37.139
Opal laughs again.

07:35:37.200 --> 07:35:39.720
No, I died a long time ago.

07:35:39.779 --> 07:35:43.439
I created my one animus gift, and then

07:35:43.439 --> 07:35:45.419
had a long, happy normal life as an ice

07:35:45.419 --> 07:35:45.779
wing.

07:35:45.840 --> 07:35:48.659
I just left a bit of my spirit in the

07:35:48.659 --> 07:35:50.819
ring to keep track of the visions and

07:35:50.819 --> 07:35:52.979
have this last conversation when the ring

07:35:52.979 --> 07:35:53.759
has finished its work.

07:35:53.819 --> 07:35:56.880
I can't believe your original queen

07:35:56.880 --> 07:36:00.119
agreed to this, Snowfall says, holding up

07:36:00.119 --> 07:36:01.259
her talon with a ring on it.

07:36:01.319 --> 07:36:03.360
She fully did not.

07:36:03.419 --> 07:36:04.619
Opal says.

07:36:04.680 --> 07:36:07.020
Why do you think I made the enchantment

07:36:07.020 --> 07:36:07.560
the way it is?

07:36:07.619 --> 07:36:10.319
She became queen before she was ready too

07:36:10.319 --> 07:36:13.259
and she was so scared, and furious all

07:36:13.259 --> 07:36:13.560
the time.

07:36:13.680 --> 07:36:16.619
She asked me for an animous gift that

07:36:16.619 --> 07:36:18.360
would let her spy on all her enemies.

07:36:18.419 --> 07:36:21.479
Both outside the kingdom and inside her

07:36:21.479 --> 07:36:22.080
own tribe.

07:36:22.139 --> 07:36:24.240
I made her this instead.

07:36:24.299 --> 07:36:25.919
Wow.

07:36:25.979 --> 07:36:28.979
Snowfall touches the opal lightly with

07:36:28.979 --> 07:36:29.520
one claw.

07:36:29.639 --> 07:36:32.340
I can't believe she didn't execute you

07:36:32.340 --> 07:36:34.319
the moment she realized she couldn't take

07:36:34.319 --> 07:36:34.680
it off.

07:36:34.740 --> 07:36:36.900
That's probably what I would have done.

07:36:36.959 --> 07:36:38.700
She adds ruefully.

07:36:38.759 --> 07:36:41.040
No, you wouldn't have.

07:36:41.099 --> 07:36:42.959
Oble says with certainty.

07:36:43.020 --> 07:36:45.299
You would have thrown me in the dungeon

07:36:45.299 --> 07:36:46.200
like she did.

07:36:46.259 --> 07:36:49.259
And then, after a few weeks, if the ring

07:36:49.259 --> 07:36:51.900
worked the way I enchanted it to, you'd

07:36:51.900 --> 07:36:53.639
have forgiven me, like she did.

07:36:53.700 --> 07:36:55.500
A few weeks?

07:36:55.560 --> 07:36:58.619
Snowfall lifts her chin proudly, and

07:36:58.619 --> 07:37:00.000
sweeps her tail across the floor.

07:37:00.060 --> 07:37:03.419
I learned all my vision lessons in just a

07:37:03.419 --> 07:37:03.779
few days.

07:37:03.840 --> 07:37:07.139
Maybe you were closer to Reddy than even

07:37:07.139 --> 07:37:09.299
you realized, Opal says.

07:37:09.360 --> 07:37:12.180
Snowfall looks down at the ice below her

07:37:12.180 --> 07:37:14.040
feet. and hesitates for a moment.

07:37:14.099 --> 07:37:15.779
What if...

07:37:15.779 --> 07:37:18.540
What if I'm not sure I am ready?

07:37:18.540 --> 07:37:19.560
she asks.

07:37:19.619 --> 07:37:22.080
Maybe I need a few more visions.

07:37:22.139 --> 07:37:24.840
No, Obal says.

07:37:24.959 --> 07:37:26.340
The ring is magic.

07:37:26.459 --> 07:37:28.740
It knows exactly how much you need.

07:37:28.860 --> 07:37:31.799
There's just one more you have to see.

07:37:31.860 --> 07:37:35.159
Suddenly, she is standing right in front

07:37:35.159 --> 07:37:37.680
of Snowfall and she rests her talons on

07:37:37.680 --> 07:37:38.819
Snowfall's temples.

07:37:38.880 --> 07:37:42.419
And then, Snowfall is.

07:37:42.659 --> 07:37:44.819
Not snowfall anymore.

07:37:44.880 --> 07:37:47.580
But her mother instead.

07:37:47.639 --> 07:37:50.580
Queen Glacier is flying in from a meeting

07:37:50.580 --> 07:37:52.860
with Blaise, thinking about what a

07:37:52.860 --> 07:37:54.959
cheerful, brain dead goose that sandwing

07:37:54.959 --> 07:37:55.259
is.

07:37:55.380 --> 07:37:57.240
Below her in the courtyard.

07:37:57.360 --> 07:38:00.060
She sees Dragonette's playing, and she

07:38:00.060 --> 07:38:01.799
lands on one of the upper ledges to watch

07:38:01.799 --> 07:38:02.040
them.

07:38:02.099 --> 07:38:05.939
Three of them are her daughters, Crystal

07:38:05.939 --> 07:38:09.180
Snowfall, and Tiny Mink, who tries to

07:38:09.180 --> 07:38:10.979
keep up with the other two, but keeps

07:38:10.979 --> 07:38:12.060
getting stuck in snow banks.

07:38:12.119 --> 07:38:14.639
They're playing some kind of made up

07:38:14.639 --> 07:38:14.880
game.

07:38:14.939 --> 07:38:17.340
Glacier can't figure out the rules from

07:38:17.340 --> 07:38:17.700
up here.

07:38:17.759 --> 07:38:20.639
But it involves a lot of running, and

07:38:20.639 --> 07:38:22.380
defending particular corners of the

07:38:22.380 --> 07:38:24.479
courtyard, and snowballs are flying

07:38:24.479 --> 07:38:24.779
everywhere.

07:38:24.840 --> 07:38:28.200
Mink tumbles into another pile of snow

07:38:28.200 --> 07:38:30.779
and snowfall grabs her, lifting her to

07:38:30.779 --> 07:38:31.740
sit on snowfall's back.

07:38:31.799 --> 07:38:34.979
Come on, we can't let them win, she

07:38:34.979 --> 07:38:35.459
shouts.

07:38:35.520 --> 07:38:38.099
She hurtles across the courtyard at

07:38:38.099 --> 07:38:41.099
ferocious speed, even with mink clinging

07:38:41.099 --> 07:38:43.200
to her shoulders, and tackles one of the

07:38:43.200 --> 07:38:44.939
other ice wings before he can throw a

07:38:44.939 --> 07:38:45.959
snowball into her corner.

07:38:46.020 --> 07:38:49.380
She rolls over him, slides him back

07:38:49.380 --> 07:38:51.779
toward his team, bowling 2 of them over

07:38:51.779 --> 07:38:54.540
when he crashes into them, and leaps up

07:38:54.540 --> 07:38:56.700
with her wings spread wide, to block

07:38:56.700 --> 07:38:58.259
another snowball from another direction.

07:38:58.319 --> 07:39:01.380
Back in the middle of the courtyard.

07:39:01.439 --> 07:39:04.380
Crystal is standing still and yawning.

07:39:04.439 --> 07:39:05.939
And is it time for lunch yet?

07:39:06.000 --> 07:39:06.779
She calls.

07:39:06.840 --> 07:39:11.159
No, Snowfall shouts back, fending off

07:39:11.159 --> 07:39:13.319
another snowball, and flinging one of her

07:39:13.319 --> 07:39:14.700
own into her opponent's face.

07:39:14.759 --> 07:39:18.000
After this, you're going to quiz me on my

07:39:18.000 --> 07:39:19.139
kingdom geography.

07:39:19.200 --> 07:39:19.860
Remember?

07:39:19.919 --> 07:39:23.099
Crystal sighs elegantly and wanders over

07:39:23.099 --> 07:39:24.000
to the nearest bench.

07:39:24.119 --> 07:39:25.979
If you say so.

07:39:26.220 --> 07:39:29.700
The sun warms glaciers wings as she

07:39:29.700 --> 07:39:30.180
watches them.

07:39:30.240 --> 07:39:33.240
Her 3 perfect dragonettes.

07:39:33.360 --> 07:39:36.900
Crystals, serenity, makes affectionate

07:39:36.900 --> 07:39:39.599
loveliness, and snowfalls indomitable

07:39:39.599 --> 07:39:40.200
ferocity.

07:39:40.259 --> 07:39:42.779
She loves them so much.

07:39:42.840 --> 07:39:45.180
She's already decided she won't fight

07:39:45.180 --> 07:39:45.900
them for the throne.

07:39:45.959 --> 07:39:48.840
Whichever one decides to challenge her

07:39:48.840 --> 07:39:50.939
first, she'll step aside and let them

07:39:50.939 --> 07:39:51.240
have it.

07:39:51.299 --> 07:39:53.639
She hopes it's snowfall.

07:39:53.700 --> 07:39:56.759
She loves them all, but Snowfall will

07:39:56.759 --> 07:39:58.319
fight for this kingdom like nobody else

07:39:58.319 --> 07:39:58.619
will.

07:39:58.680 --> 07:40:01.200
She has them growing up to do first.

07:40:01.259 --> 07:40:03.419
And Glacier hopes to pay more attention

07:40:03.419 --> 07:40:04.799
to her after the war is over.

07:40:04.919 --> 07:40:09.119
But even now, watching her, Glacier can

07:40:09.119 --> 07:40:11.099
see what a great queen snowfall could

07:40:11.099 --> 07:40:11.279
be.

07:40:11.340 --> 07:40:14.040
Bing Queen is not easy.

07:40:14.099 --> 07:40:17.939
Glacier is often exhausted, frustrated

07:40:17.939 --> 07:40:19.799
confused, uncertain.

07:40:19.860 --> 07:40:22.319
She worries for her tribe all the time

07:40:22.319 --> 07:40:25.259
and she has inexplicable nightmares about

07:40:25.259 --> 07:40:25.860
night wings.

07:40:25.919 --> 07:40:28.860
She has to work hard to seem confident in

07:40:28.860 --> 07:40:29.400
front of the tribe.

07:40:29.459 --> 07:40:32.040
The crown would be too much.

07:40:32.099 --> 07:40:33.959
For crystal or mink.

07:40:34.020 --> 07:40:35.099
It would crush them.

07:40:35.159 --> 07:40:37.919
Glacier knows perfectly well that the

07:40:37.919 --> 07:40:40.080
same is true of Blaze and the Sandwing

07:40:40.080 --> 07:40:42.299
Throne, but she plans to be a strong ally

07:40:42.299 --> 07:40:44.580
to help her hold it, if Blaze can get

07:40:44.580 --> 07:40:46.139
herself together and win the war.

07:40:46.200 --> 07:40:49.560
But snowfall is strong enough to rule a

07:40:49.560 --> 07:40:50.819
kingdom and do it well.

07:40:50.880 --> 07:40:52.919
Glacier is sure of it.

07:40:52.979 --> 07:40:55.860
Snowfall earns her place at the top of

07:40:55.860 --> 07:40:57.840
the dragonette side of the wall day after

07:40:57.840 --> 07:41:01.200
day, and she struggles, and cares, and

07:41:01.200 --> 07:41:04.020
tries, and fights, and that to the ice

07:41:04.020 --> 07:41:04.680
wings need.

07:41:04.740 --> 07:41:07.619
We're going to be all right.

07:41:07.680 --> 07:41:09.299
Glacier thanks.

07:41:09.360 --> 07:41:11.759
Feeling her shoulders relaxed for the 1st

07:41:11.759 --> 07:41:12.360
time in a while.

07:41:12.479 --> 07:41:15.299
Watching snowfall fills her with hope.

07:41:15.360 --> 07:41:17.159
No matter what happens.

07:41:17.220 --> 07:41:19.439
I'll be able to leave the tribe in the

07:41:19.439 --> 07:41:19.979
right talons.

07:41:20.040 --> 07:41:22.799
The courtyard faint away.

07:41:22.860 --> 07:41:25.979
Snowfall wipes the tears from her snout.

07:41:26.099 --> 07:41:29.580
Thank you, she says to Wopal.

07:41:29.639 --> 07:41:33.060
I just made the magic, Opal says with

07:41:33.060 --> 07:41:33.900
another shrug.

07:41:33.900 --> 07:41:35.880
You had to walk the visions.

07:41:36.000 --> 07:41:38.340
She holds out one talon.

07:41:38.400 --> 07:41:40.619
And now, you're done.

07:41:40.680 --> 07:41:43.380
Shouldn't I keep it a bit longer?

07:41:43.439 --> 07:41:44.819
Snowfall asks.

07:41:44.939 --> 07:41:47.700
So I can see what happens to the dragons

07:41:47.700 --> 07:41:48.900
who are going to Pantala.

07:41:49.020 --> 07:41:52.139
It doesn't work that way, Oble says.

07:41:52.259 --> 07:41:55.439
The gift of vision serves its purpose, and

07:41:55.439 --> 07:41:56.520
then it disappears again.

07:41:56.580 --> 07:41:59.159
Until the next dragon comes along who

07:41:59.159 --> 07:41:59.580
needs it?

07:41:59.639 --> 07:42:02.580
Snowfall slides the ring off.

07:42:02.639 --> 07:42:05.400
She can't believe how easily it moves

07:42:05.400 --> 07:42:07.380
after all those days of wrestling with

07:42:07.380 --> 07:42:07.560
it.

07:42:07.680 --> 07:42:11.099
Now it feels too big again, wobbling

07:42:11.099 --> 07:42:11.819
around her claw.

07:42:11.880 --> 07:42:14.939
She gives it to Opal, who puts it back in

07:42:14.939 --> 07:42:15.840
the empty niche.

07:42:15.900 --> 07:42:19.380
Dark eyes slides across the hole, and the

07:42:19.380 --> 07:42:22.799
words, gift of vision vanish, until the

07:42:22.799 --> 07:42:24.180
ring is completely hidden.

07:42:24.240 --> 07:42:27.360
Good luck, Obal says with a smile.

07:42:27.419 --> 07:42:31.740
Snowfall woke up late in the morning.

07:42:31.799 --> 07:42:33.959
She'd finally had a real night to sleep

07:42:33.959 --> 07:42:36.659
in the royal bed despite the tiny snuggle

07:42:36.659 --> 07:42:38.099
monster who'd climbed in beside her

07:42:38.099 --> 07:42:38.639
during the night.

07:42:38.700 --> 07:42:40.560
Mink was still asleep.

07:42:40.619 --> 07:42:43.560
One wing flopped over snowfall's snout.

07:42:43.619 --> 07:42:46.680
The ring was gone, which didn't surprise

07:42:46.680 --> 07:42:46.860
her.

07:42:46.919 --> 07:42:51.180
Stupid magic, she thought, but didn't

07:42:51.180 --> 07:42:51.419
really feel.

07:42:51.479 --> 07:42:54.419
She would miss the visions she realized.

07:42:54.540 --> 07:42:55.799
A little bit.

07:42:55.860 --> 07:42:58.860
She preferred being herself. always

07:42:58.860 --> 07:43:01.860
snowfall, but it felt oddly empty to

07:43:01.860 --> 07:43:03.479
think she'd never get to walk in someone

07:43:03.479 --> 07:43:04.799
else's talons again.

07:43:04.860 --> 07:43:07.919
Mother believed in me after all.

07:43:07.979 --> 07:43:10.979
She didn't just choose me because she

07:43:10.979 --> 07:43:11.819
couldn't have crystal.

07:43:11.880 --> 07:43:14.279
She thought I was the right choice.

07:43:14.400 --> 07:43:18.000
Snowfall moved makes wing off her face

07:43:18.000 --> 07:43:20.880
and rolled out of bed. outside the

07:43:20.880 --> 07:43:21.180
window.

07:43:21.240 --> 07:43:23.819
The sun was up, and ice wings were

07:43:23.819 --> 07:43:24.659
darting through the sky.

07:43:24.720 --> 07:43:27.119
Each one catching the light like a flying

07:43:27.119 --> 07:43:27.419
star.

07:43:27.540 --> 07:43:31.020
Beyond them, snowfall could see the ocean

07:43:31.020 --> 07:43:33.900
all that moving, glittering water between

07:43:33.900 --> 07:43:37.020
here and the lost continent of Pantala.

07:43:37.080 --> 07:43:39.840
Lynx was out there somewhere, flying to

07:43:39.840 --> 07:43:41.819
meet the rest of the dragons whose talons

07:43:41.819 --> 07:43:42.959
held the fate of the world.

07:43:43.020 --> 07:43:45.720
I hope they survive.

07:43:45.779 --> 07:43:47.819
They better survive.

07:43:47.880 --> 07:43:50.580
Or I'm going to be so furious at them.

07:43:50.700 --> 07:43:53.880
I hope they stop Queen Wasp and a breath

07:43:53.880 --> 07:43:54.419
of evil.

07:43:54.479 --> 07:43:57.240
I hope I see Skye and Ren again.

07:43:57.360 --> 07:44:00.240
And send you on cricket, and all the rest

07:44:00.240 --> 07:44:00.599
of them.

07:44:00.659 --> 07:44:04.020
I hope we're doing enough to save the

07:44:04.020 --> 07:44:04.139
world.

07:44:04.259 --> 07:44:08.700
Epilogue.

07:44:08.819 --> 07:44:12.360
Raven crept through the tunnel, listening

07:44:12.360 --> 07:44:14.759
for any sign she was being followed, but

07:44:14.759 --> 07:44:15.900
she couldn't hear anyone behind her.

07:44:15.959 --> 07:44:19.259
The darkness pressed in like panther fur

07:44:19.259 --> 07:44:20.580
brushing the hairs on her arms.

07:44:20.639 --> 07:44:23.459
But she knew the path to the abyss well

07:44:23.459 --> 07:44:24.720
enough to navigate without sight.

07:44:24.840 --> 07:44:27.720
And as she got closer, She could see the

07:44:27.720 --> 07:44:29.400
dim green glow that came from its

07:44:29.400 --> 07:44:29.819
depths.

07:44:29.880 --> 07:44:33.060
She could also see the skeletal figure

07:44:33.060 --> 07:44:34.919
that huddled by the edge of the glow.

07:44:34.979 --> 07:44:38.639
He crouched so close to the terrifying

07:44:38.639 --> 07:44:40.619
drop, it made Raven dizzy.

07:44:40.680 --> 07:44:42.540
He didn't turn toward her.

07:44:42.599 --> 07:44:45.720
His eyes were always fixed on the chasm.

07:44:45.779 --> 07:44:48.360
Fall, she whispered.

07:44:48.419 --> 07:44:49.979
I brought you food.

07:44:50.040 --> 07:44:52.380
She set her little bundle down as close

07:44:52.380 --> 07:44:53.220
to him as she dared.

07:44:53.340 --> 07:44:55.560
Then stepped back, out of reach.

07:44:55.619 --> 07:44:59.220
It had been a long time since Vol threw

07:44:59.220 --> 07:45:01.560
someone into the abyss, but that was most

07:45:01.560 --> 07:45:03.299
likely because no one else dared to

07:45:03.299 --> 07:45:04.139
approach him anymore.

07:45:04.200 --> 07:45:07.979
Only Raven, who came, even though it was

07:45:07.979 --> 07:45:11.220
forbidden, and his brother, Mole, who was

07:45:11.220 --> 07:45:13.259
allowed to keep him alive, but never

07:45:13.259 --> 07:45:14.099
allowed to speak of him.

07:45:14.220 --> 07:45:16.919
Can you hear it?

07:45:16.979 --> 07:45:19.740
Bull said, in his shivery rasp of a

07:45:19.740 --> 07:45:19.919
voice.

07:45:20.040 --> 07:45:22.080
He still didn't look at her.

07:45:22.139 --> 07:45:23.639
He never did.

07:45:23.700 --> 07:45:27.720
I think so, Raven said, sitting on one of

07:45:27.720 --> 07:45:28.619
the rock formations.

07:45:28.680 --> 07:45:32.340
I mean, I hear something, but I don't

07:45:32.340 --> 07:45:33.060
know what it's saying.

07:45:33.119 --> 07:45:34.319
Do you?

07:45:34.380 --> 07:45:37.799
The whispers reached the upper caves

07:45:37.799 --> 07:45:40.680
winding like long, clinging spider webs

07:45:40.680 --> 07:45:41.819
around the people of the village.

07:45:41.880 --> 07:45:45.240
She knew they could hear it too, from the

07:45:45.240 --> 07:45:47.159
way they flinched, or hunched their

07:45:47.159 --> 07:45:49.020
shoulders, or hurried away from one

07:45:49.020 --> 07:45:49.319
another.

07:45:49.380 --> 07:45:52.319
But no one would talk about it, except

07:45:52.319 --> 07:45:52.919
Mole.

07:45:52.979 --> 07:45:57.299
It's growing, he said softly.

07:45:57.360 --> 07:45:59.400
It's reaching.

07:45:59.520 --> 07:46:02.099
Soon it will be now.

07:46:02.159 --> 07:46:05.099
But it needs.

07:46:05.279 --> 07:46:07.200
He trailed off.

07:46:07.259 --> 07:46:09.000
Needs what?

07:46:09.060 --> 07:46:10.680
Raven asked.

07:46:10.740 --> 07:46:13.740
Suddenly, Bull whipped his head around

07:46:13.740 --> 07:46:16.020
and met her eyes for the 1st time in

07:46:16.020 --> 07:46:16.259
years.

07:46:16.319 --> 07:46:19.560
Raven jumped and nearly fled back into

07:46:19.560 --> 07:46:19.919
the dark.

07:46:19.979 --> 07:46:22.860
His eyes were nothing like they'd been

07:46:22.860 --> 07:46:25.319
when he was just her friend's funny older

07:46:25.319 --> 07:46:25.979
brother.

07:46:26.040 --> 07:46:29.580
Now they were haunted, and overlaid with

07:46:29.580 --> 07:46:32.159
a green shimmer, and they seemed to look

07:46:32.159 --> 07:46:32.880
right through her.

07:46:32.939 --> 07:46:36.180
It needs a dragon.

07:46:36.240 --> 07:46:37.740
He hissed.

07:46:37.799 --> 07:46:39.180
A dragon?

07:46:39.240 --> 07:46:41.880
Raven curled her fingers around the rough

07:46:41.880 --> 07:46:43.200
edges of the stone below her.

07:46:43.259 --> 07:46:45.240
Any dragon?

07:46:45.299 --> 07:46:48.060
She wanted to run away, screaming.

07:46:48.180 --> 07:46:50.580
But if something was changing in the

07:46:50.580 --> 07:46:52.979
abyss, Vol would be the only one who

07:46:52.979 --> 07:46:54.720
could tell her and she had to know.

07:46:54.779 --> 07:47:00.540
You must find the dragon, Bull said, and

07:47:00.540 --> 07:47:02.520
now his voice was like the crawling cave

07:47:02.520 --> 07:47:05.819
centipedes, 1000s of them, with 1000000s

07:47:05.819 --> 07:47:08.220
of scuttling legs crossing her skin.

07:47:08.279 --> 07:47:10.619
Bring it the dragon.

07:47:10.680 --> 07:47:12.419
Save the village.

07:47:12.540 --> 07:47:16.259
Wait, Raven said, as he turned back

07:47:16.259 --> 07:47:17.040
toward the abyss.

07:47:17.159 --> 07:47:18.540
What does that mean?

07:47:18.659 --> 07:47:20.040
Save the village.

07:47:20.099 --> 07:47:20.639
From what?

07:47:20.700 --> 07:47:23.520
Find the dragon.

07:47:23.819 --> 07:47:26.880
Roll said, leaning toward the glow.

07:47:26.939 --> 07:47:29.040
Bring it here.

07:47:29.099 --> 07:47:34.500
He let out a long, slithering breath that

07:47:34.500 --> 07:47:36.720
twined around the whispers from below.

07:47:36.779 --> 07:47:41.520
Or everyone you know will die.

07:47:41.639 --> 07:47:48.299
A guide to the dragons of Pentala.

07:47:48.360 --> 07:47:50.819
Hive wings.

07:47:50.880 --> 07:47:52.259
Description.

07:47:52.319 --> 07:47:56.700
Red, yellow. and or orange, but always

07:47:56.700 --> 07:47:59.459
mixed with some black scales, 4 wings.

07:47:59.520 --> 07:48:03.299
Abilities, vary from dragon to dragon.

07:48:03.419 --> 07:48:06.599
Examples include deadly stingers that can

07:48:06.599 --> 07:48:08.880
extend from their wrists to stab their

07:48:08.880 --> 07:48:11.939
enemies, Venom in their teeth or claws.

07:48:12.000 --> 07:48:15.360
A paralyzing toxin that can immobilize

07:48:15.360 --> 07:48:15.840
their prey.

07:48:15.959 --> 07:48:19.259
Others can spray boiling acid from a

07:48:19.259 --> 07:48:20.400
stinger on their tails.

07:48:20.520 --> 07:48:23.639
Queen, Queen Wasp.

07:48:23.700 --> 07:48:26.340
Silk wings.

07:48:26.400 --> 07:48:27.840
Description.

07:48:27.900 --> 07:48:30.959
Silkwing dragonettes are born wingless

07:48:30.959 --> 07:48:33.540
but go through a metamorphosis at age 6

07:48:33.540 --> 07:48:37.200
when they develop 4 huge wings and silk

07:48:37.200 --> 07:48:39.779
spinning abilities, as beautiful and

07:48:39.779 --> 07:48:42.900
gentle as butterflies, with scales in any

07:48:42.900 --> 07:48:45.419
color under the sun, except black.

07:48:45.479 --> 07:48:50.099
Abilities. can spin silk from glands on

07:48:50.099 --> 07:48:52.500
their wrists to create webs or other

07:48:52.500 --> 07:48:55.500
woven articles, can detect vibrations

07:48:55.500 --> 07:48:57.360
with their antennae to assess threats.

07:48:57.419 --> 07:49:01.020
Queen, Queen Wasp.

07:49:01.080 --> 07:49:04.439
The last Silkwing Queen, before the tree

07:49:04.439 --> 07:49:06.659
wars, was Queen Monarch.

07:49:06.720 --> 07:49:09.119
Leaf wings.

07:49:09.180 --> 07:49:10.619
Description.

07:49:10.680 --> 07:49:13.439
Wiped out during the tree wars with the

07:49:13.439 --> 07:49:16.200
hive wings, but while they lived, this

07:49:16.200 --> 07:49:18.479
tribe had green and brown scales, and

07:49:18.479 --> 07:49:20.099
wings shaped like leaves.

07:49:20.159 --> 07:49:21.779
Abilities.

07:49:21.840 --> 07:49:25.020
Could absorb energy from sunlight, and

07:49:25.020 --> 07:49:26.459
were accomplished gardeners.

07:49:26.520 --> 07:49:29.759
Some were rumored to have unusual control

07:49:29.759 --> 07:49:30.720
over plants.

07:49:30.840 --> 07:49:32.520
Queen.

07:49:32.639 --> 07:49:35.819
Last known queen of the leaf wings was

07:49:35.819 --> 07:49:39.720
Queen Sequoia, about 50 years ago, at the

07:49:39.720 --> 07:49:41.040
time of the tree wars.

